      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. it feels like we're just watching a slow motion car crash and there's nothing anyone can do to stop it. everything i try to plan for the future just feels like a joke because there won't even be a stable world to live in in 30 years. what's even the point of trying anymore?",
