    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard because everyone keeps telling me to \"stay positive\" or \"do my part,\" but that feels so delusional. like, why bother building a life, or making connections, or even just staying around to see the end of it all? if the end is inevitable, why is it seen as wrong to just skip the whole struggle?",
