    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"walking away from it all\"... it's just hard to find the words for it. it's not even that i'm sad, it's just that everything feels so heavy and useless. like, if you know the ship is sinking, why stay on board and drown slowly? is it really so crazy to want to just find some peace before it all goes wrong?",
